Name: Description
Teen Births: <g class="gr_ gr_3 gr-alert gr_gramm gr_inline_cards gr_run_anim Grammar only-ins doubleReplace replaceWithoutSep" id="3" data-gr-id="3">Number</g> of births to teenage mothers younger than 20 years old, per 1,000 teenage girls aged 15 to 19. Citywide births represent the total number of teen births to occur in New York City. Borough and community district totals represent teen births to NYC residents only.

Name: Source Notes
Notes
Teen Births: Vital Statistics combines three years of data to provide live births for teenage mothers by community district (for example 2017 = 2015, 2016, and 2017). Borough and city totals represent data for one year.
